{"tid":1391133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八號風球下　一個人的絕食抗議","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:56:27.000Z","uid":212249,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49dff156eaf9f26f7af918f9c61d4b9e4a475603","tid":1391133,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"今早一度危坐尖沙咀碼頭欄杆的馬先生，八號風球下，整天在碼頭靜坐抗議，要求政府就反對修訂逃犯條例觸發的一連串事件，設立獨立調查委員會，又呼籲市民在 8 月 5 日支持罷工。<br />\n<br />\n馬先生對《立場新聞》記者表示，自己從事販賣活雞，由昨天起沒有食東西，開始絕食。<br />\n<br />\n他說昨天葵涌警署圍堵事件，警方已經出動雷明登散彈槍，他擔心警方武力再升級，會引發更多暴力，例如可能會向示威者開槍，示威者亦可能為復仇而殺警，所以希望雙方能化解仇怨，成立獨立調查委員會調查雙方暴力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67367624_2341812089237731_6048397169289854976_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQlDO7xEkgRQWgpvaqWs5IgiqXN1UsP7ohwVeWmI3N-S7JUzlNjaMYDOEQX6TuAavEg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=cfa450537952750f265f98ac819a8e7d&amp;oe=5DA93D3A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67367624_2341812089237731_6048397169289854976_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQlDO7xEkgRQWgpvaqWs5IgiqXN1UsP7ohwVeWmI3N-S7JUzlNjaMYDOEQX6TuAavEg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dcfa450537952750f265f98ac819a8e7d%26oe%3D5DA93D3A&h=dec94a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2341812085904398/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2341812085904398%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=4f34e433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2341812085904398/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"54a2d53ad42bd4907e81c3ac0273c72685b64f50","tid":1391133,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f05da577d5988ecfd8a6ead6ba896e69200470f4","tid":